"Zhihui Xiaoxiang" 2021 China International Rail Transit and Equipment Manufacturing Industry Talent Summit-Rolling News-Hunan Daily Net-Huasheng Online Hunan Daily December 10(All-media reporter Zhou Zhiheng) On the 9th,"Zhihui Xiaoxiang" 2021 China International Rail Transit and Equipment Manufacturing Industry Talent Summit opened in Zhuzhou. Wang Cheng, member of the Standing Committee of the Provincial Party Committee and Minister of the Organization Department of the Provincial Party Committee, attended the launching ceremony and delivered a speech. Wang Cheng pointed out that holding the talent summit is an important measure to implement the spirit of the Central Talent Work Conference and the 12th Provincial Party Congress, demonstrating Hunan 's emphasis on talents and its thirst for talents.With the sincerity of talents. Hunan has a fine tradition of knowing talents, loving talents and respecting talents, a broad platform to help talent development, and environmental conditions to achieve a better life. In recent years, Hunan has deeply implemented the talent-led development strategy. Guided by the Furong Talent Action Plan, it has built a working pattern of attracting and retaining talents in the whole chain. It has become a fertile land for talent growth and achievements, a hot land for innovation and entrepreneurship, and a land suitable for living and industry. At present, Hunan is fully implementing the strategic positioning and mission of "three highs and four new". It will further open the door to attract talents, introduce better policies, concentrate more resources and create better conditions for talent innovation and entrepreneurship, and expect outstanding talents from all walks of life to jointly gather wisdom for Hunan's high-quality development. Changsha, Zhuzhou, Xiangtan pavilions and Hunan Free Trade Pilot Zone pavilions, provincial science and technology department, provincial industry and information department,The provincial department of human resources and social security issued a list of key needs for scientific and technological innovation in advanced manufacturing related industries, a list of talent needs for intelligent manufacturing industries, and a list of young talent needs for postdoctoral mobile stations in intelligent manufacturing industries.
